fields.label: Show Title
fields.name: show_engagement_title
fields.instructions: This will display the title set on top of this page and will render it on top of the engagement section.

sub_fields.label: About Engagement Feature
sub_fields.message: This feature will allow you to add an image on the left and some text on the right or vice versa. You can also choose to add a video which will open in a lightbox. The image will then have a color overlay and a play button over it. Use this option to feature a big event for instance.

sub_fields.label: Items Per Row
sub_fields.name: engagement_videos_per_row
sub_fields.instructions: Please choose the amount of videos per row.

sub_fields.label: Items Per Row
sub_fields.name: engagement_statistics_per_row
sub_fields.instructions: Please choose the amount of statistics per row.
